---
title: Zesty Bison Meatballs and Pasta with Ricotta, Garlic Bread and Fresh Salad
description: Not your average pasta, this recipe ups the ante with savoury meatballs seasoned with a zesty garlic spice blend as well as creamy ricotta. A fresh side salad brings balance while herb and garlic toasties add crunch and the ultimate scarpetta for that saucy plate!
